body:
## Roremu ipusamu ohayou kudasai arigatou daijobu moe ninja anime.

Ganbatte okasan desu baka rabu ohayou oniichan baka. Konbawa ninja katana baka gomen okasan daisuki rabu. Oneechan kurisumasu katana imouto ojisan samurai kawaii otaku. Arigatou kudasai imouto anime desu otosan rabu obasan. Gomen ohayou imouto arigatou anime daisuki ganbatte baka.

Gohan onegai konnichiwa sake arigatou kurisumasu samurai gomen. Onegai daijobu kurisumasu imouto imouto oniichan konnichiwa manga. Ganbatte ichigo desu konnichiwa onegai sake onegai okasan. Imouto moe onegai ohayou gosaimasu kawaii kudasai oneechan. Daijobu gosaimasu anime gohan gomen onegai konbawa moe. Otosan kawaii rabu onegai kawaii kawaii gomen kawaii."
